          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdeqN1hXHUODWZ8IFUwItlOZuTpnQi58R4vjYLubIzLOQJQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "As I live the life of addiction I feel like I am always treated less than human. That was until I was recommended by a friend in recovery to give this clinic a chance . By the grace of god I was taken in and cared for the same day. From the security to the counselors and the medical staff I was treated like the human being that I am . Being recommend to this program was one of the best things anyone could have shared with me . I\u2019d like to recommend you to join me in recovery at : West Medical Group an O.T.P. Just for you.Thank you for reading my story.\u2764\ufe0f God Bless!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VQS3VnZjdLdVplWFNnEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0xc8c354813f7ea5b1!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEPKugf7KuZeXSg%7C%7C?hl=en",
