          "description": "My wife & I been @west midtown since 2018 April it is a great place everyone there is amazing & to the person who says when you sign up they make you wait to get medicated for a few days well that\u2019s a flat out lie\nThey medicate you the same day within 2 hours of you coming in the building your medicated\nHope all is well everyone\nI recommend west midtown to anyone is a great place & all staff & security are amazing\nHave blessed night",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKWldrNVRibVpCTlZZM1RIZHdNSGQzUmxwclpFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc8c354813f7ea5b1!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjJZWk5TbmZBNVY3THdwMHd3RlprZEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "9 months ago",
